  "description": "An unofficial Foundry VTT implementation of The Mecha Hack, a roll-under d20 mecha combat RPG published by Absolute Tabletop. Features mecha actors with stats (Power, Mobility, System, Presence), reactor die degradation, enemy sheets with boss mode, and initiative based on stat tests.",
